The following code provided by <a rel="nofollow noreferrer" href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/uwp/audio-video-camera/codec-query">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/uwp/audio-video-camera/codec-query</a> results in an exception "An unhandled win32 exception occurred in MediaElementControl.exe [16416]
<br>CodecQuery thisCodecQuery = new CodecQuery();
<br>IReadOnlyList&lt;CodecInfo&gt; thisReadOnlyList;
<br>thisReadOnlyList = await thisCodecQuery.FindAllAsync(CodecKind.Audio, CodecCategory.Decoder, string.Empty);
